# Crypto Paper Trading Bot 🚀

A Telegram-based cryptocurrency paper trading bot that allows users to simulate trading without using real money.

The bot uses cryptocurrency market data from Binance API and provides basic trading functionality through Telegram commands.

## Features

- 📈 Real-time cryptocurrency price tracking
- 💰 Virtual cryptocurrency buying and selling
- 📊 Portfolio management
- 📝 Trade history tracking
- 🔌 Binance API integration
- 🤖 Telegram bot interface

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Telegram Bot API
- Binance API
- REST API

## Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/lykrew/crypto-paper-trading-bot.git

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

Create a .env file:

BOT_TOKEN=
BINANCE_API_KEY=
BINANCE_SECRET=

Run the bot:

python main.py
Available Commands
/start - Start the bot
/price - Get cryptocurrency price
/buy - Buy cryptocurrency
/portfolio - View portfolio
